All employees of FT Teams are prohibited from employment in other teams or in the FIA.
All employees are prohibited from spectating or listening into other radios as to prevent an unfair advantage.
Constructors may not use any other car besides their main car.
In the event of a crash, if the driver can not get back to the pitstop and repair the car **THEY ARE CURRENTLY IN**, they are considered as DNF, as is that team.
